approach :- kadens algorithem

// brute-force approach  (using 2 loop's)

1. sbse phele 1st loop total array ko traverse krege

2. 2nd loop i se remaing array ko traverse krega & each time element ko sum m add krega

3. each time sum ko max variable se compare krenge

4. inside loop ke each complete traversal pr sum ki value ko 0 se reset krenge


// optimal approach (kaden's algo)

1. loop array ka traversal krega & array-element ko sum m add krega 

2. ab sum ko each time max se check krenge

3. yadi sum ki value -ive ho jati h to sum=0 krenge
   (kyoki sum ke -ive hone pr yadi usko next element se add krenge to sum next element ki value ko overall decrease hoga-
    -isse accha h ki only next +ive element ko hi sum m add kre)
